title: Kyler Not Getting Traded?
description:
Field, RG3, Louis, McShay, and Darlington discuss what trades they want to see in the first round of next weeks NFL Draft, Kayvon Thibodeaux’s draft range, Kyler Murray’s quest for a long-term deal, Deebo’s trade value and more.
